AUDIO: 'to it down in the description as well. Now, the first thing I want to highlight is why dynamic workflows. We touched on it at the beginning. Hey, it\'s better for complex task, but why is Claude normally not good enough for this thing? Well, that is because the longer Claude works on a complex task in a single'

[06:04] [scene:talk]
