VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'remember my video a couple of days ago where I showed you Grill Me Codex, bringing Codex into the equation, this is something I talked about there as well, right? Claude isn\'t great at evaluating its own work, especially if you\'re telling it to evaluate work'

