VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'within the same session. Like you\'re in the same context window. Like it\'s not great at it. And then lastly, goal drifting. Again, keep beating this drum, complex task, goal drifting is going to be a big'

[06:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'thing. We have to handle this. We can\'t do these things in one session. And so, creating a workflow, a dynamic workflow, helps combat these by orchestrating separate Claude sub-agents with their own context windows and focused, isolated goals.'

